## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of up-to-date and comprehensive data on human cloning. The ethical and social implications of cloning are complex and evolving, and this report may not capture all perspectives or the latest developments in the field. Additionally, the sources used may have inherent biases based on their publication context and the authors' viewpoints. Further research and ongoing ethical discussions are necessary to fully understand the implications of human cloning.